                                                ("You've been invited by "
                                                    ++ DisplayName.nameAndId user.name userId
                                                    ++ " to join town-collab! "
                                                )
                                            , Email.Html.a
                                                [ Email.Html.Attributes.href inviteUrl ]
                                                [ Email.Html.text "Click here to join" ]
